    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧨 <strong>涡轮战车，火力全开</strong><br>通过涡轮、加速器和爆炸性改装升级车辆。这不仅是赛车，更是战争机器。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>强力Boss战</strong><br>在剧情模式中挑战致命Boss，征服废土！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>战斗竞速</strong><br>撞击、射击、爆破！这不是普通比赛，是一场生存战争！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>升级与自定义</strong><br>从刹车系统到巨大涡轮，自由打造你的毁灭战车！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>动态赛道</strong><br>多样化地图与天气系统，影响你的驾驶方式——白天、夜晚、雨、雾应有尽有。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>多种游戏模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情战役 – 约8小时内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvE挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地分屏 &amp; 在线对战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速竞速模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竞技场模式 – 生存并击毁一切！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>适合哪些玩家？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turbo Sloths适合喜欢以下的玩家：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twisted Metal、Crossout、FlatOut、SnowRunner<br>热爱改装与强化车辆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢毁灭性竞速</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要混乱中找乐趣</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢打Boss的剧情模式！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💬 <strong>玩家评价</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这就像加装了涡轮的Mad Max！”<br>“疯狂又爽快的赛车游戏。”<br>“自FlatOut之后最燃的一次体验。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏁 <strong>准备出发了吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉你对赛车的所有印象。<br>打造你的战争机器，冲上赛道，把敌人炸成废铁！<br><strong>Turbo Sloths 等你来战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
